# [AVTCORE](../wg/avtcore.html)

## Summary

This interim meeting of AVTCORE covered the status and ongoing discussions for several drafts: RTP Payload Format for SKIP, Green Metadata, RTP over QUICK, and Viewport Region of Interest for Volumetric Media. Key discussions revolved around addressing IESG ballot comments for SKIP, clarifying congestion control strategies for RTP over QUICK, and refining the technical specifications for immersive media delivery. No drafts were adopted during this session, but authors were given specific feedback and action items to revise their documents.

